Your Highness.

15
00:02:00,580 --> 00:02:01,500
Mr. Su?

16
00:02:03,460 --> 00:02:04,700
What are you doing here?

17
00:02:06,220 --> 00:02:07,540
The Crown Prince's wedding is near.

18
00:02:07,620 --> 00:02:09,100
The Ministry of Justice
is responsible for security.

19
00:02:09,420 --> 00:02:10,500
So, it has been quite busy.

20
00:02:10,860 --> 00:02:11,700
As for me,

21
00:02:11,700 --> 00:02:12,940
I was just planning to take a stroll
in the Imperial Garden

22
00:02:12,940 --> 00:02:14,260
during official duties.

23
00:02:14,500 --> 00:02:15,300
I didn't expect

24
00:02:15,380 --> 00:02:16,500
to meet you here.

25
00:02:19,460 --> 00:02:20,740
I'm here to relax

26
00:02:21,020 --> 00:02:23,100
and also think about Chuan's wedding.

27
00:02:27,220 --> 00:02:28,620
Chuan's wedding is approaching.

28
00:02:28,940 --> 00:02:30,940
But he's been sad.

29
00:02:31,540 --> 00:02:32,820
I'm not sure

30
00:02:33,660 --> 00:02:34,900
if his marriage

31
00:02:35,060 --> 00:02:36,580
with the Shangguan Family is good

32
00:02:36,940 --> 00:02:38,380
or bad for him.

33
00:02:41,340 --> 00:02:42,380
It seems like everyone,

34
00:02:42,380 --> 00:02:43,620
including myself,

35
00:02:44,180 --> 00:02:45,900
is pushing him to make a choice.

36
00:02:46,540 --> 00:02:48,060
Have you considered postponing

37
00:02:48,500 --> 00:02:50,100
the Crown Prince's wedding

38
00:02:50,180 --> 00:02:52,100
to give him more time
to decide, Your Highness?

39
00:02:53,140 --> 00:02:54,380
That's an option.

40
00:02:59,700 --> 00:03:00,420
But

41
00:03:01,500 --> 00:03:02,860
the Crown Prince's wedding
is a major event

42
00:03:03,020 --> 00:03:04,500
of the court.

43
00:03:04,620 --> 00:03:05,940
It's not something we can easily change.

44
00:03:08,300 --> 00:03:09,660
If that's the case,

45
00:03:10,500 --> 00:03:12,100
I do have a solution.

46
00:03:15,100 --> 00:03:16,260
I remember

47
00:03:16,260 --> 00:03:17,740
you only mentioned it to me back then

48
00:03:17,980 --> 00:03:19,420
and didn't take further action.

49
00:03:20,580 --> 00:03:23,100
As for the matter of using Hongde
to postpone the Crown Prince's wedding,

50
00:03:23,300 --> 00:03:25,100
no one would know about this.

51
00:03:26,260 --> 00:03:28,980
Besides, we didn't even
go to Hongde this time.

52
00:03:29,420 --> 00:03:31,620
But Su Rongqing took
preemptive action by using Hongde.

53
00:03:31,940 --> 00:03:32,980
More importantly,

54
00:03:33,140 --> 00:03:33,940
how did he know

55
00:03:33,940 --> 00:03:35,380
about your intention
to postpone the wedding?

56
00:03:35,380 --> 00:03:36,460
That's the problem.

57
00:03:37,620 --> 00:03:38,580
This excuse is exactly

58
00:03:38,580 --> 00:03:40,260
the same as what I thought before.

59
00:03:41,300 --> 00:03:42,300
Why use this reason

60
00:03:42,300 --> 00:03:43,700
to postpone the Crown Prince's wedding?

61
00:03:46,100 --> 00:03:47,260
And in this new life,

62
00:03:48,180 --> 00:03:50,180
he seems to know everything in advance.

63
00:03:53,780 --> 00:03:55,060
Is it all just a coincidence?

64
00:03:56,260 --> 00:03:57,540
So you are saying

65
00:03:58,420 --> 00:04:00,020
- Su Rongqing has also returned.
